  _enemyName: The Hollow King
  _description: 'The first true lord of the Hollow, once a noble king who sought
    to control the corruption. Now he IS the corruption.


    PHASE 1 (100-70%):
    Awakening - Predictable attacks with Strength buildup.

    PHASE 2 (70-30%):
    Corruption Surge - Mass corruption, multi-hits, applies Vulnerability.

    PHASE
    3 (<30%): Desperate Onslaught - Enraged +50% damage, relentless multi-attacks.


    ARENA:
    +5 Corruption to team each turn.'
